node.contents: Don't worry , it seems that most of the threads are just waiting, they will become busy when requests arrive to your Jetty server.

astNode.text: Don't worry , it seems that most of the threads are just waiting, they will become busy when requests arrive to your Jetty server.

node.contents: Most web servers keep a thread pool of a certain size, to not create/delete thread objects every time.

astNode.text: Most web servers keep a thread pool of a certain size, to not create/delete thread objects every time.

node.contents: So check your Jetty configuration to see the configured size of your thread pool, and compare with the number of waiting threads.

astNode.text: So check your Jetty configuration to see the configured size of your thread pool, and compare with the number of waiting threads.
